WEBVTT

01:52.690 --> 01:57.570
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.500 --> 02:01.900
[Episode 36]

02:47.310 --> 02:48.910
Take my lady away for preparations.

02:48.910 --> 02:49.630
Yes.

03:00.830 --> 03:01.520
Boss.

03:01.720 --> 03:03.570
Everyone left is here.

03:03.670 --> 03:05.470
We have at most half an hour left.

03:07.680 --> 03:09.150
Half an hour

03:09.740 --> 03:10.650
is enough.

03:11.800 --> 03:12.800
Pass my order.

03:13.590 --> 03:15.030
Anyone who comes this way

03:15.290 --> 03:16.710
will be killed without mercy.

03:16.710 --> 03:17.340
Yes.

03:31.760 --> 03:33.020
Spread out and search.

03:33.730 --> 03:34.970
We must find Fan Yun.

03:35.150 --> 03:35.990
Yes.

03:36.090 --> 03:37.490
Let's go. Follow me.

03:50.840 --> 03:52.730
♪ Why oh why ♪

03:52.750 --> 03:54.030
♪ Is the path of destiny ♪

03:54.060 --> 03:56.690
♪ So bittersweet? ♪

03:57.420 --> 03:59.329
♪ My gaze rests on ♪

03:59.350 --> 04:03.500
♪ The fading lights,
with nowhere to return ♪

04:03.530 --> 04:07.080
♪ Inundated with bitter pain ♪

04:07.630 --> 04:08.920
What's wrong, Master?

04:07.910 --> 04:10.390
♪ My obsession still wouldn't surrender ♪

04:09.560 --> 04:10.560
Are you okay?

04:11.130 --> 04:16.800
♪ In the end,
my love is still unrequited ♪

04:18.120 --> 04:19.589
♪ I could have ♪

04:19.620 --> 04:21.209
♪ Played every trick in the book ♪

04:21.240 --> 04:24.600
♪ But I chose painstaking devotion ♪

04:24.780 --> 04:26.430
♪ Never caging my love ♪

04:26.100 --> 04:26.980
It's okay.

04:26.460 --> 04:30.680
♪ Even if I had to
trudge through a thousand miles ♪

04:27.550 --> 04:28.500
Keep going.

04:30.810 --> 04:34.880
♪ Henceforth, I shall wander the world,
plucking petals and holding the moon ♪

04:35.140 --> 04:38.460
♪ Listen to the wind and admire the moon
for days on end ♪

04:38.630 --> 04:44.560
♪ Accept that I'm not your happiness ♪

04:44.630 --> 04:47.350
♪ Let go of what's before me ♪

04:47.370 --> 04:51.330
♪ Consider this the best ending ♪

04:51.450 --> 04:53.930
♪ I disdain everything
in the vast universe ♪

04:53.960 --> 04:58.310
♪ So why do I care for
a single glance from you? ♪

04:58.340 --> 05:00.970
♪ Drinking a pot of the past ♪

05:00.990 --> 05:05.850
♪ I toast to my withering self
as the curtains fall ♪

05:05.870 --> 05:12.100
♪ And you don't know the reason why ♪

05:19.210 --> 05:21.920
♪ Let go of what's before me ♪

05:21.940 --> 05:25.900
♪ Consider this the best ending ♪

05:26.020 --> 05:28.500
♪ I disdain everything
in the vast universe ♪

05:28.530 --> 05:32.890
♪ So why do I care for
a single glance from you? ♪

05:32.909 --> 05:35.540
♪ Drinking a pot of the past ♪

05:35.570 --> 05:40.420
♪ I toast to my withering self
as the curtains fall ♪

05:40.440 --> 05:46.670
♪ And you don't know the reason why ♪

05:47.030 --> 05:57.180
♪ And you don't know the reason why ♪

06:09.720 --> 06:10.490
I...

06:11.930 --> 06:13.070
Where am I?

06:33.159 --> 06:34.270
You're awake.

06:36.240 --> 06:37.000
You...

06:37.870 --> 06:39.040
Zheng Shi.

06:41.800 --> 06:43.120
Why am I here?

06:43.960 --> 06:45.360
What exactly do you want?

06:45.480 --> 06:46.480
What I want

06:46.620 --> 06:48.140
has always been just you.

06:53.390 --> 06:54.240
Today,

06:56.040 --> 06:57.460
I want you to be my wife.

07:34.600 --> 07:35.400
It's Qi Zheng.

07:36.190 --> 07:37.190
It's Qi Zheng!

07:44.680 --> 07:46.040
Let go of me!

07:46.070 --> 07:47.600
I know where Zheng Xian kept

07:47.950 --> 07:49.470
all his explosives.

07:52.430 --> 07:53.560
I have ways to set off

07:56.560 --> 07:58.360
all the ones he failed to set off.

07:59.560 --> 08:00.620
Zheng Shi,

08:01.040 --> 08:02.390
are you crazy?

08:03.480 --> 08:04.860
If you leave here,

08:06.000 --> 08:07.520
more people will die.

08:11.990 --> 08:12.950
The first one

08:12.980 --> 08:14.130
will be Qi Zheng.

08:20.240 --> 08:21.080
Like you said,

08:22.800 --> 08:24.310
I am a madman.

08:29.720 --> 08:30.630
You...

08:31.550 --> 08:32.419
Zheng Shi.

08:33.690 --> 08:34.600
You...

08:36.919 --> 08:38.669
How did you become like this?

08:44.080 --> 08:45.390
Become like what?

08:47.770 --> 08:49.050
In this world,

08:49.670 --> 08:52.270
I only care about
how you and Grandfather feel.

08:53.450 --> 08:55.360
If they are both gone,

08:56.790 --> 08:59.080
it doesn't matter what I become.

09:29.650 --> 09:30.730
Zheng Shi,

09:30.760 --> 09:32.440
why must you do this?

09:32.920 --> 09:34.850
Don't you know that some things

09:36.710 --> 09:38.460
simply can't be forced?

09:41.180 --> 09:42.340
What does it matter?

09:44.040 --> 09:45.440
A life that you dislike

09:46.440 --> 09:47.770
will pass by in a moment.

09:50.150 --> 09:51.750
But a moment you like

09:53.440 --> 09:55.440
can last you for a lifetime.

10:19.200 --> 10:20.120
Here.

10:20.490 --> 10:21.630
Put this on.

10:27.120 --> 10:28.000
No need.

10:30.480 --> 10:31.840
I have

10:34.910 --> 10:36.870
my own belonging here.

10:38.580 --> 10:40.440
I will wear my own hair accessory.

11:14.200 --> 11:15.960
It's almost time.

11:16.590 --> 11:18.200
Tidy up and come out.

11:29.490 --> 11:30.980
♪ If women are akin to blossoms ♪

11:31.020 --> 11:33.360
♪ Can they be cherished tenderly? ♪

11:33.520 --> 11:36.690
♪ For whom do they hide tears silently? ♪

11:36.970 --> 11:39.190
♪ How could one bear to lay blame? ♪

11:39.210 --> 11:41.580
♪ Time runs wild with reckless haste ♪

11:41.800 --> 11:45.500
♪ Never mind that
fate dyes pureness crimson red ♪

11:45.620 --> 11:46.960
♪ For whom does ♪

11:46.980 --> 11:49.150
♪ This phoenix flower bloom? ♪

11:49.180 --> 11:53.150
♪ Love fills my years,
and my heart remains true ♪

11:53.380 --> 11:55.430
♪ Let all worldly longing fade away ♪

11:54.440 --> 11:55.960
Put on the Phoenix Crown.

11:55.460 --> 11:57.850
♪ Fall deep within a single dream ♪

11:57.830 --> 11:58.620
Otherwise,

11:58.170 --> 12:06.770
♪ Wait till a breath of wind arrives ♪

11:59.520 --> 12:01.160
I'll blow up the bridge.

12:20.850 --> 12:22.040
Qi Zheng...

13:00.360 --> 13:01.910
Qi Zheng, watch out!

13:07.710 --> 13:08.900
You should be looking at me.

13:08.900 --> 13:10.140
Look at me.

13:22.430 --> 13:24.520
The auspicious time has arrived.

13:27.810 --> 13:28.850
Fan Yun.

13:28.880 --> 13:29.960
Think again.

13:29.980 --> 13:31.840
Are you marrying me today, or not?

13:47.030 --> 13:50.090
First bow to Heaven and Earth;
a perfect couple is made.

13:55.720 --> 13:56.630
Qi Zheng,

13:58.390 --> 14:00.390
if you can't make it out alive today,

14:01.510 --> 14:03.200
I shall perish with you.

14:15.560 --> 14:17.150
♪ Spring winds, autumn rain ♪

14:17.170 --> 14:18.650
♪ Flowers bloom for a single season ♪

14:18.670 --> 14:20.670
♪ Fallen petals turn into mud ♪

14:20.150 --> 14:23.150
Second bow to the parents;
joining in marriage.

14:20.700 --> 14:23.150
♪ It's never ♪

14:23.170 --> 14:26.310
♪ The ending I crave ♪

14:27.390 --> 14:29.590
♪ I'd be the wick lit up ♪

14:29.670 --> 14:31.390
♪ For you each night ♪

14:31.490 --> 14:33.430
♪ Burning myself bright ♪

14:32.670 --> 14:33.710
Zheng Shi.

14:33.460 --> 14:36.050
♪ Beside you as you hold the brush ♪

14:35.400 --> 14:37.090
You can't threaten us.

14:36.080 --> 14:38.900
♪ Till every streak of ink fades away ♪

14:40.560 --> 14:42.650
♪ I search and search through all days ♪

14:42.670 --> 14:43.900
♪ Lingering on with unwilling heart ♪

14:43.920 --> 14:46.000
♪ What does a final choice matter? ♪

14:46.030 --> 14:48.530
♪ In the moment of looking back ♪

14:48.550 --> 14:51.530
♪ This life is worth it ♪

14:52.220 --> 14:54.890
♪ When no dawn can be seen ahead ♪

14:54.920 --> 14:58.760
♪ Who are the dream-walkers? ♪

14:58.960 --> 15:00.960
♪ Facing the light ♪

14:59.750 --> 15:03.390
Husband and wife bow to each other;
tying the knot.

15:00.980 --> 15:04.730
♪ Singing a long song along the way ♪

15:04.900 --> 15:07.510
♪ Tear the dark night apart ♪

15:07.530 --> 15:09.210
♪ Turn my whole heart ♪

15:09.240 --> 15:11.240
♪ Into an ever-burning bright lamp light ♪

15:11.260 --> 15:13.930
♪ Live up to every year ♪

15:13.950 --> 15:17.180
♪ With fiery passion ♪

15:17.330 --> 15:20.110
♪ Even if I merge into ♪

15:20.130 --> 15:21.840
♪ The stream of stars in the end ♪

15:21.860 --> 15:24.130
♪ With thousands of miles between us ♪

15:24.150 --> 15:30.170
♪ I never fade away within your eyes ♪

15:32.110 --> 15:34.390
Drink the sweet dew tea from crossed cups,

15:34.390 --> 15:38.120
become a married couple,
and be deeply in love with no doubts.

15:46.760 --> 15:50.620
Drink the sweet dew tea together,
and be deeply in love with no doubts.

15:55.330 --> 15:57.300
Drink this cup of sweet dew tea,

15:57.800 --> 15:59.090
and you will be my wife.

16:07.350 --> 16:08.260
Zheng Shi!

16:10.440 --> 16:12.040
You have disappointed me so.

16:13.670 --> 16:15.030
We were once

16:15.550 --> 16:16.600
friends

16:17.390 --> 16:18.510
and confidants.

16:20.560 --> 16:22.200
You knew very well that

16:22.790 --> 16:23.550
I...

16:29.330 --> 16:30.970
I don't love you at all.

16:43.660 --> 16:45.310
This is your last chance.

16:47.280 --> 16:49.140
If you don't drink this cup of tea,

16:50.290 --> 16:51.320
I'm afraid someone

16:51.320 --> 16:52.980
won't leave here alive today.

17:10.089 --> 17:11.890
Tell your men to stop now.

17:11.920 --> 17:13.270
Please don't fight anymore.

17:13.270 --> 17:15.109
How many people have to die
for you to be satisfied?

17:15.109 --> 17:16.109
Zheng Shi!

17:16.109 --> 17:17.280
One more, me.

17:22.089 --> 17:23.369
What do you mean,

17:23.940 --> 17:25.069
Zheng Shi?

17:36.870 --> 17:38.400
My name sounds so beautiful

17:39.560 --> 17:40.870
when you say it.

17:45.370 --> 17:46.310
I really want to drink

17:46.310 --> 17:47.880
the sweet dew tea made by you,

17:47.880 --> 17:48.740
Fan Yun.

18:00.210 --> 18:01.340
The sweet dew tea...

18:06.420 --> 18:08.350
I have already had it with Qi Zheng.

18:20.810 --> 18:21.970
So,

18:23.860 --> 18:25.660
I won't have it with anyone else.

18:45.630 --> 18:46.770
I lost

18:51.400 --> 18:52.710
this bet to you.

18:57.790 --> 18:58.640
Fan Yun.

19:06.830 --> 19:08.230
Since you're unwilling,

19:10.290 --> 19:11.160
this time,

19:14.160 --> 19:15.690
I will return your freedom.

19:17.550 --> 19:20.260
♪ Let go of what's before me ♪

19:20.290 --> 19:24.250
♪ Consider this the best ending ♪

19:24.370 --> 19:26.850
♪ I disdain everything
in the vast universe ♪

19:26.870 --> 19:31.230
♪ So why do I care for
a single glance from you? ♪

19:31.260 --> 19:33.890
♪ Drinking a pot of the past ♪

19:33.910 --> 19:38.760
♪ I toast to my withering self
as the curtains fall ♪

19:38.790 --> 19:45.020
♪ And you don't know the reason why ♪

19:54.660 --> 19:56.630
Zheng Shi! Zheng Shi!

20:02.900 --> 20:04.380
♪ I could have ♪

20:04.410 --> 20:06.000
♪ Played every trick in the book ♪

20:06.030 --> 20:09.380
♪ But I chose painstaking devotion ♪

20:09.560 --> 20:11.220
♪ Never caging my love ♪

20:11.240 --> 20:15.470
♪ Even if I had to
trudge through a thousand miles ♪

20:13.800 --> 20:15.360
Zheng Shi!

20:15.590 --> 20:19.670
♪ Henceforth, I shall wander the world,
plucking petals and holding the moon ♪

20:19.930 --> 20:23.240
♪ Listen to the wind and admire the moon
for days on end ♪

20:23.420 --> 20:29.340
♪ Accept that I'm not your happiness ♪

20:25.160 --> 20:26.000
Fan Yun!

20:29.420 --> 20:32.130
♪ Let go of what's before me ♪

20:32.160 --> 20:36.120
♪ Consider this the best ending ♪

20:36.240 --> 20:38.720
♪ I disdain everything
in the vast universe ♪

20:38.740 --> 20:43.100
♪ So why do I care for
a single glance from you? ♪

20:39.510 --> 20:40.750
I always thought that

20:41.070 --> 20:43.200
pursuing the ultimate freedom

20:43.130 --> 20:45.760
♪ Drinking a pot of the past ♪

20:43.200 --> 20:45.200
was the happiest thing in life.

20:45.780 --> 20:50.630
♪ I toast to my withering self
as the curtains fall ♪

20:46.960 --> 20:48.760
Until Grandfather passed away,

20:49.480 --> 20:51.720
I gradually started to understand
what you said.

20:50.660 --> 20:56.890
♪ And you don't know the reason why ♪

20:53.460 --> 20:55.070
At that time, I thought,

20:55.550 --> 20:56.890
it's not too late,

20:57.350 --> 20:58.750
at least I still have you.

21:00.550 --> 21:01.440
So for the first time, I thought

21:01.440 --> 21:03.300
about someone other than myself,

21:03.820 --> 21:06.530
♪ Let go of what's before me ♪

21:04.030 --> 21:06.030
and wondered what I could do for you.

21:06.560 --> 21:10.520
♪ Consider this the best ending ♪

21:08.110 --> 21:09.070
But I realized

21:10.200 --> 21:12.590
I still failed to hold onto anything.

21:10.640 --> 21:13.120
♪ I disdain everything
in the vast universe ♪

21:13.140 --> 21:17.500
♪ So why do I care for
a single glance from you? ♪

21:14.350 --> 21:15.410
I wanted to tell you

21:16.830 --> 21:18.790
that you were the one who took my life.

21:17.530 --> 21:20.160
♪ Drinking a pot of the past ♪

21:20.160 --> 21:21.480
That way,

21:20.180 --> 21:25.040
♪ I toast to my withering self
as the curtains fall ♪

21:21.480 --> 21:24.010
I could become
the most special person to you,

21:24.790 --> 21:26.830
making you remember me forever

21:25.060 --> 21:31.290
♪ And you don't know the reason why ♪

21:26.830 --> 21:27.960
and grieve for me.

21:29.680 --> 21:32.370
But I was afraid
you would really be heartbroken.

21:32.370 --> 21:41.630
♪ And you don't know the reason why ♪

21:34.440 --> 21:35.960
Maybe this is for the best.

21:38.680 --> 21:39.720
Fan Yun.

23:07.590 --> 23:08.960
Get in.

23:10.080 --> 23:10.840
Hurry up.

23:10.860 --> 23:11.930
Get in.

23:16.790 --> 23:18.590
Since Elder Zheng entrusted me,

23:19.160 --> 23:20.490
it's my responsibility

23:20.550 --> 23:23.150
to select a new clan leader
for the Zheng family

23:23.270 --> 23:26.200
to ensure the stability
and prosperity of Jing City.

23:26.310 --> 23:27.390
Recently,

23:28.360 --> 23:29.380
I have also witnessed

23:29.380 --> 23:31.180
Zheng Xi's courage and bravery,

23:31.230 --> 23:32.450
which is why I recommend her

23:32.450 --> 23:34.620
as a candidate for
the clan leader of the Zheng family.

23:34.620 --> 23:35.220
Zheng Xi,

23:37.530 --> 23:38.440
tell me,

23:39.640 --> 23:41.120
are you willing to help me

23:41.270 --> 23:42.330
rebuild Jing City?

23:58.480 --> 23:59.570
Elders,

24:00.220 --> 24:02.750
I have indeed been withdrawn

24:02.780 --> 24:04.310
and quiet since childhood.

24:05.720 --> 24:07.200
But I also studied and grew up

24:07.200 --> 24:08.720
with my brothers.

24:09.310 --> 24:11.110
Although I never dreamed of

24:11.360 --> 24:13.630
serving the Nine Cities

24:13.660 --> 24:14.940
like my ancestors did,

24:16.420 --> 24:18.590
since I met Gate Cdr. Fan,

24:19.080 --> 24:20.320
I realized

24:20.680 --> 24:22.000
that women

24:22.030 --> 24:24.670
can be just as courageous as men.

24:25.900 --> 24:26.790
Women

24:26.820 --> 24:29.100
can also have their own careers

24:29.120 --> 24:30.190
and ambitions.

24:31.200 --> 24:32.660
Now, Jing City is in ruins,

24:32.920 --> 24:35.190
and the people are suffering.

24:35.620 --> 24:37.250
I am not willing to retreat.

24:37.960 --> 24:38.590
So,

24:39.210 --> 24:41.170
if I say I don't want to now,

24:41.920 --> 24:43.060
it would be a lie.

24:44.110 --> 24:46.140
Yes.

24:47.440 --> 24:48.030
Good.

24:49.090 --> 24:51.680
After hearing Zheng Xi's heartfelt words,

24:52.400 --> 24:53.720
what do you all think?

24:54.640 --> 24:56.880
I second that.

24:59.330 --> 25:00.240
From today on,

25:01.090 --> 25:03.520
you are the new clan leader
of the Zheng family.

25:03.520 --> 25:06.350
I hope you remain determined
and unyielding.

25:09.670 --> 25:11.500
Yes, Your Excellency.

25:19.330 --> 25:20.730
You said he was poisoned?

25:21.130 --> 25:23.090
Yes, Boss...

25:24.490 --> 25:25.620
I mean, Zheng Shi,

25:26.480 --> 25:27.750
was badly poisoned

25:28.350 --> 25:30.210
before the succession ceremony.

25:30.310 --> 25:31.440
How was he poisoned?

25:32.120 --> 25:33.910
He was ambushed by a hidden arrow

25:33.910 --> 25:35.570
that scratched his right arm.

25:36.350 --> 25:37.320
The arrowhead

25:37.590 --> 25:38.790
was dipped in poison.

25:40.140 --> 25:42.480
It must have been Zheng Xian's doing.

25:44.800 --> 25:46.320
If he knew he was poisoned,

25:47.200 --> 25:48.530
why did he ignore it?

25:49.300 --> 25:51.230
This poison is unique to Jing City.

25:51.520 --> 25:53.980
One will die a few days
after it takes effect.

25:55.070 --> 25:56.730
After searching everywhere,

25:57.020 --> 25:59.880
the antidote turned out to be
a Jing City specialty,

25:59.920 --> 26:00.920
the sweet dew tea.

26:02.260 --> 26:04.850
He knew the sweet dew tea
could cure the poison.

26:04.850 --> 26:06.360
If he had drunk it earlier,

26:06.790 --> 26:08.000
he wouldn't have

26:08.270 --> 26:09.530
deteriorated so much.

26:25.190 --> 26:25.920
Is your wound

26:26.370 --> 26:27.330
going to be okay?

26:28.760 --> 26:29.830
As long as you are here,

26:29.830 --> 26:30.890
I won't die.

26:37.120 --> 26:38.250
Are you alright?

26:40.280 --> 26:42.080
It seems you still care about me.

26:43.080 --> 26:44.080
I just wonder when

26:44.530 --> 26:46.960
I will be able to drink
the tea brewed by your own hands,

26:46.960 --> 26:47.680
Fan Yun.

26:56.350 --> 26:58.160
If you don't drink this tea,

26:59.310 --> 27:00.270
I'm afraid someone

27:00.270 --> 27:01.930
won't leave here alive today.

27:16.610 --> 27:18.770
You didn't have to die.

27:20.970 --> 27:23.410
Why did you refuse to drink it?

28:00.090 --> 28:01.090
Your Excellency.

28:05.180 --> 28:07.240
Today we are not master and minister.

28:07.980 --> 28:09.240
Just sit down and talk.

28:23.810 --> 28:25.340
Why are you drinking alone?

28:28.110 --> 28:29.570
Is something on your mind?

28:42.550 --> 28:43.590
Your Excellency.

28:44.610 --> 28:46.020
I have one request

28:46.640 --> 28:48.270
that I hope you will agree to.

28:51.160 --> 28:52.920
I want to stay in Jing City.

28:54.650 --> 28:56.180
You are the gate commander.

28:57.090 --> 28:59.690
It's only right for you
to stay here for a while.

29:00.790 --> 29:01.940
How long do you need?

29:05.870 --> 29:08.000
Jing City has just been through turmoil,

29:08.000 --> 29:09.660
and the people are unsettled.

29:10.160 --> 29:12.000
Zheng Xi and I are discussing

29:12.570 --> 29:14.230
how to revitalize this place.

29:15.680 --> 29:16.550
As for

29:17.400 --> 29:19.000
how long it will take,

29:20.160 --> 29:22.360
I cannot give you an estimate right now.

29:32.350 --> 29:34.480
Let's discuss this when you are sober.

29:35.060 --> 29:35.700
Sit.

29:36.590 --> 29:38.110
I am very sober now.

29:38.130 --> 29:39.550
Why discuss it another day?

29:39.550 --> 29:40.750
I told you to sit down.

29:40.960 --> 29:42.550
Your Excellency, I hope you

29:42.550 --> 29:44.080
can give me an answer today.

29:45.010 --> 29:47.230
-As the gate commander of Jing City...
-I told you to sit down.

29:47.230 --> 29:49.890
Or I'll dismiss you right now,
believe it or not.

29:55.950 --> 29:56.990
You wouldn't.

29:58.750 --> 30:00.550
What makes you think I wouldn't?

30:01.920 --> 30:03.050
I am human too.

30:03.900 --> 30:05.110
I also have uncontrollable emotions.

30:05.110 --> 30:06.910
What makes you think I wouldn't?

30:13.960 --> 30:15.820
Fan Yun, let me ask you something.

30:16.830 --> 30:18.090
Do you want to stay here

30:19.480 --> 30:20.810
for Jing City,

30:23.480 --> 30:24.960
or for Zheng Shi?

30:35.120 --> 30:36.120
Your Excellency,

30:38.900 --> 30:40.490
how could you think that?

30:45.020 --> 30:46.380
Have you really no clue

30:46.660 --> 30:47.990
what kind of person I am

30:48.350 --> 30:50.150
and what I think about every day?

30:52.110 --> 30:53.040
These days,

30:53.370 --> 30:54.600
all I've been thinking about

30:54.600 --> 30:56.010
is what will become of Jing City.

30:56.010 --> 30:58.740
And not about Zheng Shi's
funeral arrangements?

31:00.810 --> 31:02.870
You want to stay in Jing City as family

31:02.870 --> 31:04.070
to keep vigil for him.

31:08.030 --> 31:08.750
Right?

31:14.360 --> 31:15.400
Answer me.

31:17.560 --> 31:18.840
I told you to speak.

31:20.030 --> 31:21.390
I told you to speak!

31:39.730 --> 31:42.590
You haven't thought it through yourself,
have you?

31:51.610 --> 31:54.100
Thinking of him as a thorn in your heart

31:54.990 --> 31:56.750
makes him a thorn in mine too.

31:57.850 --> 31:59.890
I also hate the way I am now.

32:01.350 --> 32:02.480
But I just want to...

32:04.200 --> 32:06.000
I just want to be selfish for once

32:07.740 --> 32:09.290
and be your first choice.

32:20.030 --> 32:21.030
I'll wait for you.

32:44.530 --> 32:45.400
Qi Zheng...

32:47.120 --> 32:48.650
Wait for me a little longer.

32:55.670 --> 32:56.730
His Excellency...

32:58.030 --> 32:59.090
His Excellency...

32:59.360 --> 33:00.760
His Excellency has left.

33:01.680 --> 33:03.410
This is a letter he left for you.

33:03.840 --> 33:05.970
He said you probably wouldn't go back.

33:13.860 --> 33:16.090
Suyin, go back and rest first.

33:25.260 --> 33:26.100
Fan Yun,

33:27.480 --> 33:29.010
I actually wanted to ask you

33:29.700 --> 33:31.910
if you were willing to leave with me.

33:33.090 --> 33:35.090
But I know your answer.

33:36.100 --> 33:37.010
I know

33:37.600 --> 33:39.400
it's not that you're unwilling,

33:39.980 --> 33:41.220
but that you cannot.

33:41.430 --> 33:45.410
[Jing City]

33:43.340 --> 33:45.740
Now all the men
in the Zheng family are gone,

33:46.130 --> 33:47.410
Zheng Xi alone

33:47.840 --> 33:49.570
has to face the huge Jing City.

33:50.700 --> 33:52.420
Leaving only Tian Xing with her

33:52.420 --> 33:53.620
might not be enough to help.

33:53.220 --> 33:55.980
♪ My heart is unwavering ♪

33:54.890 --> 33:56.070
I know you

33:56.470 --> 33:59.980
♪ My dreams become wings ♪

33:56.480 --> 33:58.200
definitely want to stay in Jing City

33:58.200 --> 34:00.260
and leave only after seeing results.

34:00.370 --> 34:04.850
♪ What does it matter
if we fly against the wind? ♪

34:00.550 --> 34:02.200
I know all of this.

34:03.830 --> 34:05.030
But Fan Yun,

34:05.730 --> 34:08.620
♪ The most ordinary desire ♪

34:06.310 --> 34:07.840
I'm willing to wait for you.

34:08.650 --> 34:13.270
♪ Is worth lighting up ♪

34:08.760 --> 34:09.710
I'll wait until you see me more than

34:09.710 --> 34:11.030
just the governor.

34:12.170 --> 34:14.610
I'll wait for the day
you return to my side.

34:13.290 --> 34:15.920
♪ With my life ♪

34:15.670 --> 34:17.320
I'll wait, even if

34:15.940 --> 34:18.620
♪ From then on ♪

34:17.860 --> 34:19.409
that day may never come.

34:18.650 --> 34:21.679
♪ Time left a glimmer of hope ♪

34:21.909 --> 34:30.650
♪ Take it as the glory of my journey ♪

34:31.500 --> 34:37.080
♪ Face the light,
gaze ahead with brave eyes ♪

34:37.270 --> 34:41.469
♪ Let all darkness and hurt step aside ♪

34:41.489 --> 34:43.620
♪ It's unstoppable ♪

34:43.760 --> 34:49.460
♪ We ride the light and travel together ♪

34:49.679 --> 34:51.650
♪ Not considering how long the road is ♪

34:51.699 --> 34:55.699
♪ When looking back,
I'm still young and stubborn ♪

34:55.719 --> 34:59.470
♪ Let the weathered past ♪

34:59.500 --> 35:01.990
♪ The places once journeyed ♪

35:02.020 --> 35:05.600
♪ Turn into myriad lights ♪

35:05.630 --> 35:10.720
♪ Just as I expected ♪

35:14.120 --> 35:17.480
[Six months later]

35:32.280 --> 35:34.540
Didn't you think my embroidery was ugly?

35:35.550 --> 35:36.590
I said

35:37.190 --> 35:38.250
it was very unique.

35:41.040 --> 35:42.330
Why are you still here?

35:42.370 --> 35:43.400
Didn't you promise me

35:43.400 --> 35:44.730
to show me around today?

35:45.290 --> 35:46.420
You saw it yourself.

35:46.690 --> 35:47.820
My shift was changed.

35:47.820 --> 35:49.440
I can't leave until the Shen hour.

35:49.440 --> 35:50.650
The Shen hour?

35:50.760 --> 35:52.490
Do you know what day it is today?

35:52.490 --> 35:53.940
You clearly promised me.

35:53.970 --> 35:55.770
How can you break your word?

35:55.790 --> 35:56.600
Do you care...

36:13.130 --> 36:15.830
♪ Wind sheds rain like tears ♪

36:15.850 --> 36:17.070
♪ Over the whole town ♪

36:17.090 --> 36:19.590
♪ At the second our gazes meet ♪

36:19.740 --> 36:23.310
♪ Past memories roar one louder beat ♪

36:26.050 --> 36:28.530
♪ Perhaps hearts long to seek ♪

36:28.550 --> 36:29.910
♪ Etch within our fingertips ♪

36:29.940 --> 36:32.830
♪ Hear crisp footsteps echo clear ♪

36:32.850 --> 36:36.330
♪ Strike out
on a fearless dream's frontier ♪

36:35.190 --> 36:37.420
Today is your day.

36:37.740 --> 36:41.080
♪ Though fleeting years rush
without delay ♪

36:41.140 --> 36:44.160
♪ A wisp of softness
tints your brow each day ♪

36:44.190 --> 36:46.190
♪ Walk side by side with moon and sun ♪

36:46.210 --> 36:49.330
♪ When all is said and all is done ♪

36:49.350 --> 36:51.350
♪ We'll ride the ups and downs ♪

36:51.380 --> 36:53.810
♪ When deep love dwells within our eyes ♪

36:54.050 --> 36:57.070
♪ Our burning longing never dies ♪

36:57.080 --> 36:59.040
See you at the Shen hour.

36:57.200 --> 37:02.000
♪ Wander together through wind and frost ♪

37:02.030 --> 37:04.030
♪ Every dark night fades at last ♪

37:04.050 --> 37:06.580
♪ When fate resides within our sight ♪

37:06.690 --> 37:11.370
♪ Gazing toward each other's
distant light ♪

37:11.470 --> 37:14.900
♪ What do heaven and earth seek
but salvation in companionship? ♪

37:12.700 --> 37:20.840
[Jing City]

37:14.920 --> 37:18.020
♪ Don't let the sun down ♪

37:21.120 --> 37:22.400
The end of the year is approaching.

37:22.400 --> 37:24.460
The gate commander
is returning to Ling'an to report.

37:24.460 --> 37:26.630
With Sir Tian Xing staying in Jing City,

37:26.630 --> 37:28.830
you can go to Ling'an with peace of mind.

37:30.560 --> 37:32.090
With you accompanying him,

37:32.110 --> 37:33.440
I'm definitely at ease.

37:39.030 --> 37:39.970
Sirs,

37:40.350 --> 37:42.150
Liu Mu will be traveling with me.

37:42.170 --> 37:43.370
Please rest assured.

37:43.850 --> 37:44.910
You can go back now.

38:53.910 --> 38:55.820
Dad, Gao Ran,

38:57.080 --> 38:58.250
you are here too.

38:59.230 --> 39:01.160
I'm here to demand an explanation.

39:02.550 --> 39:03.800
You returned to Ling'an,

39:03.800 --> 39:05.800
but instead of going home
to tell me you are safe,

39:05.800 --> 39:07.460
you came to the mansion first.

39:07.720 --> 39:10.150
Do you know how upsetting that is?

39:14.250 --> 39:15.290
Dad...

39:16.090 --> 39:18.430
Alright, I was just teasing you.

39:19.320 --> 39:20.370
Now that you are an official,

39:20.370 --> 39:22.930
of course you have to see
His Excellency first,

39:22.930 --> 39:24.030
and then go home.

39:26.850 --> 39:28.040
Little Whirlwind.

39:35.310 --> 39:36.710
Do you still remember me?

39:39.320 --> 39:40.250
Long time no see,

39:40.820 --> 39:41.950
Little king of rods.

39:44.180 --> 39:45.230
I'm here!

39:47.320 --> 39:48.320
How have you been?

39:49.280 --> 39:50.230
Good.

39:52.590 --> 39:53.630
Dad...

39:55.620 --> 39:56.620
-Please.
-Uncle.

39:57.320 --> 39:59.530
[Firm in conviction and eager to learn]

39:57.430 --> 39:59.090
Let's all have another drink.

40:00.890 --> 40:03.040
Splendid.

40:04.480 --> 40:05.890
Let me tell you.

40:07.190 --> 40:08.750
Back in the day,

40:09.960 --> 40:11.690
when I was your age,

40:11.720 --> 40:12.590
I was with Lyu,

40:13.560 --> 40:14.440
and Zheng.

40:16.470 --> 40:17.960
The late governor led us

40:18.460 --> 40:20.160
to gallop on the battlefield,

40:20.550 --> 40:22.010
fighting north and south,

40:23.210 --> 40:24.850
never hesitating.

40:27.370 --> 40:28.080
Drink!

40:28.440 --> 40:29.680
Slow down.

40:32.090 --> 40:33.450
Let go.

40:33.510 --> 40:34.230
Eat more.

40:34.230 --> 40:34.710
Come on.

40:34.710 --> 40:35.910
-Let’s go.
-Eat more.

40:36.440 --> 40:37.500
What are you doing?

40:37.730 --> 40:39.660
We haven't had enough to drink yet.

40:40.450 --> 40:41.850
Come back and drink more.

40:43.710 --> 40:44.400
Come, eat.

40:44.400 --> 40:45.210
Come on.

40:46.030 --> 40:47.480
Come, have a bite.

40:48.620 --> 40:49.670
Lord Lyu.

40:50.310 --> 40:51.730
When did you get here?

40:52.850 --> 40:54.770
With such delicious food here,

40:54.800 --> 40:56.430
how could I be absent?

40:56.450 --> 40:57.480
That's true.

40:57.510 --> 40:58.570
He's just a foodie.

41:01.170 --> 41:02.040
Come.

41:02.830 --> 41:03.870
Zheng,

41:04.550 --> 41:06.930
the state of the Nine Cities now

41:07.440 --> 41:09.330
must be what you've wanted to see.

41:11.550 --> 41:12.440
Come.

41:12.860 --> 41:14.900
Let's have a drink together.

41:15.780 --> 41:17.010
Try this.

41:22.840 --> 41:24.360
Eat more. Come on.

41:24.380 --> 41:25.380
Eat more.

41:38.280 --> 41:39.750
When will you let Fan Yun

41:39.970 --> 41:41.330
hold a ceremony

41:42.030 --> 41:44.430
to officially acknowledge me as her uncle?

41:52.520 --> 41:54.120
Don't drink so much

41:54.230 --> 41:56.160
with your weak alcohol tolerance.

42:01.350 --> 42:03.190
Let me say a few words.

42:03.210 --> 42:05.530
Although it's a bit late,

42:05.740 --> 42:06.780
I, Fan Yun,

42:06.810 --> 42:08.930
have safely returned from Jing City.

42:09.770 --> 42:10.690
Thank you all

42:11.180 --> 42:12.440
for worrying about me.

42:13.250 --> 42:14.330
Drink.

42:14.480 --> 42:15.440
Come on.

42:15.440 --> 42:17.150
Let's all have a drink together.

42:17.150 --> 42:19.400
Good, you are indeed a heroine.

42:22.140 --> 42:22.910
Fan Yun.

42:24.270 --> 42:26.130
Yan Jiang is probably lost again.

42:26.210 --> 42:26.920
How about

42:27.780 --> 42:29.180
you go look for him for me?

42:29.880 --> 42:30.670
Me?

42:31.920 --> 42:33.370
Yes. Look,

42:33.390 --> 42:35.130
Lord Zhao keeps talking to me
about the past.

42:35.130 --> 42:36.460
I really can't get away.

42:37.330 --> 42:38.330
Okay.

42:38.960 --> 42:39.560
Oh, right.

42:39.850 --> 42:41.530
It's easy to get lost in the Phoenix Woods
on a snowy night like this.

42:41.530 --> 42:42.740
Be careful.

42:42.770 --> 42:43.840
Got it.

42:45.730 --> 42:48.230
The bookshelves in Qilin Pavilion
are like a maze.

42:48.230 --> 42:49.170
Fan Yun, I...

42:54.180 --> 42:55.230
Who called me?

43:03.620 --> 43:05.820
You're hearing things.
Hurry up and go.

43:07.070 --> 43:07.820
Alright.

43:08.130 --> 43:10.150
Then help me entertain everyone well.

43:10.150 --> 43:11.680
Okay, go ahead.

43:50.830 --> 43:53.970
♪ Watch how many flowers
bloom and wither ♪

43:54.390 --> 43:57.820
♪ Count how many springs
and autumns pass ♪

43:58.190 --> 44:00.750
♪ Why the sighs and regrets? ♪

44:06.810 --> 44:10.300
♪ Lovers wait a lifetime ♪

44:10.640 --> 44:13.830
♪ Feelings that can't be severed ♪

44:14.400 --> 44:17.150
♪ How to let go? ♪

44:23.050 --> 44:26.400
♪ All our fates were long inscribed ♪

44:26.740 --> 44:30.400
♪ How to set free grief and joy? ♪

44:30.970 --> 44:32.690
♪ Mortal life is but an ephemeral dream ♪

44:33.100 --> 44:38.650
♪ No mortal soul may rule its life ♪

44:39.030 --> 44:40.520
♪ If women are akin to blossoms ♪

44:40.560 --> 44:42.900
♪ Can they be cherished tenderly? ♪

44:43.060 --> 44:46.230
♪ For whom do they hide tears silently? ♪

44:46.510 --> 44:48.730
♪ How could one bear to lay blame? ♪

44:48.750 --> 44:51.120
♪ Time runs wild with reckless haste ♪

44:51.150 --> 44:54.850
♪ Never mind that
fate dyes pureness crimson red ♪

44:55.160 --> 44:56.500
♪ For whom does ♪

44:56.520 --> 44:58.690
♪ This phoenix flower bloom? ♪

44:58.720 --> 45:02.690
♪ Love fills my years,
and my heart remains true ♪

45:02.920 --> 45:04.970
♪ Let all worldly longing fade away ♪

45:05.000 --> 45:07.390
♪ Fall deep within a single dream ♪

45:07.410 --> 45:16.590
♪ Wait till a breath of wind arrives ♪

45:50.430 --> 45:51.240
I...

45:52.810 --> 45:53.960
I thought

45:54.750 --> 45:57.680
I would only see you
at tomorrow's morning assembly.

45:58.500 --> 46:00.160
I didn't expect you to be here.

46:03.070 --> 46:04.280
I come here

46:05.080 --> 46:06.120
every night.

46:14.080 --> 46:14.920
Qi Zheng.

46:16.620 --> 46:17.610
I'm back.

46:24.820 --> 46:26.310
♪ If women are akin to blossoms ♪

46:26.350 --> 46:28.690
♪ Can they be cherished tenderly? ♪

46:28.850 --> 46:32.020
♪ For whom do they hide tears silently? ♪

46:32.300 --> 46:34.520
♪ How could one bear to lay blame? ♪

46:34.540 --> 46:36.910
♪ Time runs wild with reckless haste ♪

46:36.940 --> 46:40.640
♪ Never mind that
fate dyes pureness crimson red ♪

46:40.950 --> 46:42.290
♪ For whom does ♪

46:41.400 --> 46:42.510
Fan Yun.

46:42.310 --> 46:44.480
♪ This phoenix flower bloom? ♪

46:43.400 --> 46:44.520
Fan Yun.

46:44.510 --> 46:48.480
♪ Love fills my years,
and my heart remains true ♪

46:48.710 --> 46:50.760
♪ Let all worldly longing fade away ♪

46:50.790 --> 46:53.180
♪ Fall deep within a single dream ♪

46:51.660 --> 46:53.090
I finally see you again.

46:53.360 --> 47:00.850
♪ Wait till a breath of wind arrives ♪

47:00.990 --> 47:02.430
I have something for you.

47:03.320 --> 47:04.360
What is it?

47:51.050 --> 47:54.400
♪ All our fates were long inscribed ♪

47:54.740 --> 47:58.400
♪ How to set free grief and joy? ♪

47:58.970 --> 48:00.690
♪ Mortal life is but an ephemeral dream ♪

48:00.990 --> 48:06.540
♪ No mortal soul may rule its life ♪

48:06.740 --> 48:08.390
♪ For whom does ♪

48:08.410 --> 48:10.580
♪ This phoenix flower bloom? ♪

48:10.610 --> 48:14.670
♪ Love fills my years,
and my heart remains true ♪
